{"type":"message","id":"dc5051ad","parentId":"43366890","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:59:25.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to read the cron task configuration file to understand what needs to be done for real-time stock price monitoring.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_720c4bc224514899a725323b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773111562784}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f654b0c","parentId":"dc5051ad","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:59:25.560Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_720c4bc224514899a725323b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 以下描述的文件都在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt；\n- 注意：TOOLS.md文件是一个例外，它的实际路径是~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md；\n- 如果存在可用脚本，优先复用，不满足当前场景时才允许创建新脚本。\n- 执行时严格按照要求的文件名称及后缀，防止执行到不存在的文件。\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘，未收盘，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n2、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n3、阅读TOOLS.md内的skill使用说明，严格按照要求使用skill；\n4、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n5、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n6、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n7、读取receiver-list.txt接受者用户列表文件，使用命令openclaw message broadcast --channel feishu --account stock --targets <user_id1> --targets <user_id2>... --message <xxx>，\n   将预警数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给列表文件中的用户；\n   - --targets <user_id> 参数可重复\n8、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773111565558}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4ef71e4","parentId":"2f654b0c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:59:29.880Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要读取相关的配置文件和脚本文件来了解如何执行这个实时股价监控任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cfa2202582344be6a9901162","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/TOOLS.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_beeba8cfe02d40849fe80195","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_527ee24b1a9341218ef88fdc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_85379e61adab4ef798c7dbde","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/receiver-list.txt"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b2be67b44fbe4c22b26de7dc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d6b93d9818584226a93c96e1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773111565561}}
{"type":"message","id":"83245559","parentId":"f4ef71e4","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:59:29.909Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cfa2202582344be6a9901162","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/TOOLS.md'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/TOOLS.md'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773111569907}}
{"type":"message","id":"263a9ff6","parentId":"83245559","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:59:29.912Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_beeba8cfe02d40849fe80195","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773111569911}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1ccd332","parentId":"263a9ff6","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:59:29.916Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_527ee24b1a9341218ef88fdc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773111569914}}
{"type":"message","id":"577b5bd0","parentId":"c1ccd332","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:59:29.922Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_85379e61adab4ef798c7dbde","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\nou_0737da20bef21e4dff04d2b83f927208\nou_144623d3a3b4a119305355db7813bb31\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773111569920}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff3dd482","parentId":"577b5bd0","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:59:29.925Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b2be67b44fbe4c22b26de7dc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773111569924}}
